data.description: 4 BR, 2.5 Bath Traditional, 2 story home located on a lovely corner lot in the delightful British Woods community. Clean & Move -in ready! Many features, including screened porch, 2-car attached garage. Hardwood floors, eat-in Kitchen, large bedrooms & closets. Ready for your personal touch. Formal Living & Dining rooms, plus fireside Den. Back-entry Laundry room, drop zone w/storage.
